                      Super Bowl MVP

                      The following market is a prop on which player will be named the Most Valuable Player (MVP) of Super Bowl 50. Statistically, this market most often is awarded to the quarterback, so the odds are heavily weighted in favor of each team's signal-caller. However, due to the fact that this Super Bowl involves the number one and two ranked defenses, several defensive players are included in the wagering market.
